org.simulationsystems.csf.distsys.core.api.distributedautonomousagents

Class DistributedAutonomousAgent

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.simulationsystems.csf.distsys.core.api.distributedautonomousagents.DistributedAutonomousAgent

  • public class DistributedAutonomousAgent
extends java.lang.Object
    This is an object in the CSF that represents a distributed autonomous agent. It is not the same as the distributed autonomous agent itself (such as a JADE agent). The implementors of this API do not have direct references to the underlying distributed autonomous agent.
    Since:
    0.1
    Version:
    0.1
    Author:
    Jorge Calderon
